				<p>Got &#8216;em in the oven right now.  Using what I have on hand and aiming for the flavor profile of a favorite cookie, I used toasted pecans instead of hazelnuts and cinnamon and cayenne in place of espresso powder.  The dough tasted terrific.</p>
	</li>
		
		
		
	
